column2: Did your previous employers ever formally discuss mental health (as part of a wellness campaign or other official communication)?
column3: Do you currently have a mental health disorder?
column4: Do you have a family history of mental illness?
column6: Do you know the options for mental health care available under your employer-provided health coverage?
column7: Does your employer offer resources to learn more about mental health disorders and options for seeking help?
column8: Does your employer provide mental health benefits as part of healthcare coverage?
column9: Have you ever sought treatment for a mental health disorder from a mental health professional?
column10: Have you had a mental health disorder in the past?
column11: Have you observed or experienced a *supportive or well handled response* to a mental health issue in your current or previous workplace?
column12: Have your previous employers provided mental health benefits?
column13: How many employees does your company or organization have?
column14: How willing would you be to share with friends and family that you have a mental illness?
column15: If a mental health issue prompted you to request a medical leave from work, how easy or difficult would it be to ask for that leave?
column16: If you have a mental health disorder, how often do you feel that it interferes with your work when being treated effectively?
column17: If you have a mental health disorder, how often do you feel that it interferes with your work when not being treated effectively (i.e., when you are experiencing symptoms)?
column18: Is your employer primarily a tech company/organization?
column19: Was your anonymity protected if you chose to take advantage of mental health or substance abuse treatment resources with previous employers?
column20: Were you aware of the options for mental health care provided by your previous employers?
column21: What country do you live in?
column22: What country do you work in?
column24: Would you bring up your *mental* health with a potential employer in an interview?
column25: Would you feel comfortable discussing a mental health issue with your coworkers?
column26: Would you have been willing to discuss your mental health with your direct supervisor(s)?
